@startuml
title QAPM - Android Performance Monitoring Control Flow

actor Developer
participant "Build System" as Build
participant "QBuildPlugin" as Plugin
participant "AspectJAppTransform" as Transform
participant "Android App" as App
participant "QAPM" as QAPM
participant "QAPMConfig" as Config
participant "QConfigManager" as ConfigMgr
participant "TracePlugin" as TracePlugin
participant "ApplicationLifeObserver" as LifecycleObs
participant "WatchMan" as WatchMan
participant "BatteryTracer" as Battery
participant "CpuTracer" as CPU
participant "MemoryTracer" as Memory
participant "FPSTracer" as FPS
participant "NetworkInstrumentation" as NetInstr
participant "Storage" as Storage
participant "NetworkSender" as Sender
participant "Backend Server" as Server

== Build Time: AOP Injection ==
Developer -> Build: Start build process
Build -> Plugin: Apply QBuildPlugin
activate Plugin
Plugin -> Plugin: Add extensions
Plugin -> Plugin: Register transform
Plugin -> Transform: Execute transform
activate Transform
Transform -> Transform: Intercept class compilation
Transform -> Transform: Inject QAPM monitoring code via ASM
Transform -> Build: Return instrumented classes
deactivate Transform
deactivate Plugin
Build -> Developer: Build complete

== Runtime: Initialization ==
App -> QAPM: Initialize QAPM
activate QAPM
QAPM -> Config: Load QAPMConfig (Builder pattern)
activate Config
Config -> ConfigMgr: Register configuration
activate ConfigMgr
ConfigMgr --> Config: Configuration stored
deactivate ConfigMgr
Config --> QAPM: Configuration ready
deactivate Config
QAPM -> LifecycleObs: Register ApplicationLifeObserver
activate LifecycleObs
LifecycleObs --> QAPM: Observer registered
deactivate LifecycleObs
QAPM -> TracePlugin: Initialize TracePlugin
activate TracePlugin
TracePlugin -> Battery: Initialize BatteryTracer (Singleton)
activate Battery
Battery --> TracePlugin: Tracer ready
deactivate Battery
TracePlugin -> CPU: Initialize CpuTracer (Singleton)
activate CPU
CPU --> TracePlugin: Tracer ready
deactivate CPU
TracePlugin -> Memory: Initialize MemoryTracer (Singleton)
activate Memory
Memory --> TracePlugin: Tracer ready
deactivate Memory
TracePlugin -> FPS: Initialize FPSTracer
activate FPS
FPS --> TracePlugin: Tracer ready
deactivate FPS
TracePlugin --> QAPM: All tracers initialized
deactivate TracePlugin
QAPM -> Storage: Initialize Storage (Singleton)
activate Storage
Storage --> QAPM: Storage ready
deactivate Storage
QAPM --> App: QAPM initialized
deactivate QAPM

== Runtime: Activity Lifecycle Monitoring ==
App -> LifecycleObs: Activity created
activate LifecycleObs
LifecycleObs -> WatchMan: onActivityCreated
activate WatchMan
WatchMan -> TracePlugin: Start lifecycle tracing
activate TracePlugin
TracePlugin -> Battery: startTrace()
activate Battery
Battery -> Battery: Begin battery monitoring
deactivate Battery
TracePlugin -> CPU: startTrace()
activate CPU
CPU -> CPU: Begin CPU monitoring
deactivate CPU
TracePlugin -> Memory: startTrace()
activate Memory
Memory -> Memory: Begin memory monitoring
deactivate Memory
TracePlugin -> FPS: startTrace()
activate FPS
FPS -> FPS: Begin FPS monitoring
deactivate FPS
deactivate TracePlugin
deactivate WatchMan
deactivate LifecycleObs

== Runtime: Network Request Monitoring ==
App -> NetInstr: Make HTTP request
activate NetInstr
NetInstr -> NetInstr: Intercept request
NetInstr -> NetInstr: Instrument HTTP call
NetInstr -> NetInstr: Collect network metrics
NetInstr -> Storage: Store network data
activate Storage
Storage -> Storage: Persist data locally
deactivate Storage
NetInstr --> App: Return response
deactivate NetInstr

== Runtime: Performance Data Collection ==
Battery -> Battery: Collect battery metrics
Battery -> Storage: Store battery data
activate Storage
Storage --> Battery: Data stored
deactivate Storage

CPU -> CPU: Collect CPU metrics
CPU -> Storage: Store CPU data
activate Storage
Storage --> CPU: Data stored
deactivate Storage

Memory -> Memory: Collect memory metrics
Memory -> Storage: Store memory data
activate Storage
Storage --> Memory: Data stored
deactivate Storage

FPS -> FPS: Collect frame rate metrics
FPS -> Storage: Store FPS data
activate Storage
Storage --> FPS: Data stored
deactivate Storage

== Runtime: Data Reporting ==
Storage -> Sender: Retrieve collected data
activate Sender
Sender -> Sender: Prepare data payload
Sender -> Server: Send performance data
activate Server
Server -> Server: Process metrics
Server --> Sender: Acknowledgment
deactivate Server
Sender -> Storage: Mark data as sent
deactivate Sender

== Runtime: Activity Lifecycle Stop ==
App -> LifecycleObs: Activity destroyed
activate LifecycleObs
LifecycleObs -> WatchMan: onActivityDestroyed
activate WatchMan
WatchMan -> TracePlugin: Stop lifecycle tracing
activate TracePlugin
TracePlugin -> Battery: stopTrace()
activate Battery
Battery -> Battery: Stop battery monitoring
Battery -> Storage: Store final battery data
activate Storage
Storage --> Battery: Data stored
deactivate Storage
deactivate Battery
TracePlugin -> CPU: stopTrace()
activate CPU
CPU -> CPU: Stop CPU monitoring
CPU -> Storage: Store final CPU data
activate Storage
Storage --> CPU: Data stored
deactivate Storage
deactivate CPU
TracePlugin -> Memory: stopTrace()
activate Memory
Memory -> Memory: Stop memory monitoring
Memory -> Storage: Store final memory data
activate Storage
Storage --> Memory: Data stored
deactivate Storage
deactivate Memory
TracePlugin -> FPS: stopTrace()
activate FPS
FPS -> FPS: Stop FPS monitoring
FPS -> Storage: Store final FPS data
activate Storage
Storage --> FPS: Data stored
deactivate Storage
deactivate FPS
deactivate TracePlugin
deactivate WatchMan
deactivate LifecycleObs

@enduml
